<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3838900>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. A–D. Acanthopharynx denticulatus Wieser, 1954, ♂. A. Head region. B. Tail region. C. Copulatory apparatus. D. Neck region. E–F. Bolbonema brevicolle Cobb, 1920, ♂. E. Neck region. F. Posterior region with tail end in surface view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3838900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3838902>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Acanthopharynx denticulatus Wieser, 1954, SEM microphotographs of ♂. A. Head oblique en face view. B. Cuticle striation at mid-body. C. Cloacal region, from a different ♂ specimen than A, B and D. D. Tail tip, showing ventral bent." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3838902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

